  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SPACEFLUX </strong>- THE ONE & ONLY<strong> FRACTAL FPS! </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>fractal space</strong>, the map contains itself. Going to the center takes you back to where you started. You can never reach the center!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1344440/extras/652ebec9e9c127159c99c0683b900450.poster.avif?t=1763264644\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1344440/extras/652ebec9e9c127159c99c0683b900450.webm?t=1763264644\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1344440/extras/652ebec9e9c127159c99c0683b900450.mp4?t=1763264644\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RECURSIVE ARENA COMBAT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn to navigate the fractals in hyper-fast PvP combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are <strong>infinite</strong> copies of the map, with a copy of <i>you</i> on each map. Be careful, don't shoot yourself in the back!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your opponents have copies too. Shoot any copy to kill them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1344440/extras/c1d118925d9ce196d79ee5267c91330c.poster.avif?t=1763264644\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1344440/extras/c1d118925d9ce196d79ee5267c91330c.webm?t=1763264644\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1344440/extras/c1d118925d9ce196d79ee5267c91330c.mp4?t=1763264644\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MORE IMPOSSIBLE SPACES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fractal space is just 1 of the 6 impossible spaces:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Horizontal Loop </strong>- the map repeats infinitely in all directions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Minimap </strong>- a mini-version of the map exists within the map. Jump inside to land back onto the map</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mirror Mode -</strong> the map is reflected and so are you </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Portals </strong>- enter a portal to another place in the map</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Vertical Loop</strong> - fall forever!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1344440/extras/cced99d19f9a0c7c0a3f835f72e304a3.poster.avif?t=1763264644\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1344440/extras/cced99d19f9a0c7c0a3f835f72e304a3.webm?t=1763264644\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1344440/extras/cced99d19f9a0c7c0a3f835f72e304a3.mp4?t=1763264644\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>HORDE MODE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The single player roguelike<strong> </strong>where you fight endless waves of heads in all impossible spaces. Can you beat <strong>Atomic Pete</strong>, or will he erase you from existence?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1344440/extras/7b338b4ae1d9c14e7763187dd6aca0cc.poster.avif?t=1763264644\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1344440/extras/7b338b4ae1d9c14e7763187dd6aca0cc.webm?t=1763264644\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1344440/extras/7b338b4ae1d9c14e7763187dd6aca0cc.mp4?t=1763264644\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2-4 Player multiplayer deathmatches</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 Fully destructible and impossible maps</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Single-player survival horde mode</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn on ‘Psychedelic Mode’ to mess with your friends</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Abilities to flip gravity, spawn decoys or disguise yourself as a box</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cosmetic gun skins for all 10 weapons</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controller & Steam Deck support</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Peer-to-peer matchmaking</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you so much for your patience and support over the last 4 years of Early Access!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >- Calin</h2>",
